column5: So as planed the voting poll was to end tonight at 7:00pm. Little Angler and myself both had 27 votes. Thanks a lot to those who voted and as far as prizes go....well im not sure. I think we both had fun and successfu camping trips. Maybe next year some more people on the site can join a activity like this.  Thanks a lot!!  Mike
Ok the both of you will have to send me your mailing address, that way I can send you both a shad rap.
